            <title>[JCR-1225] ReadOnlyIndexReaders are re-created on every access</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/JCR-1225</link>
                <project id="10591" key="JCR">Jackrabbit Content Repository</project>
                        <description>AbstractIndex.getReadOnlyIndexReader() creates a new instance on every call. The returned index reader should instead be cached and kept open as long as there are no changes on the underlying index.</description>
                <environment></environment>
